/>\n依家呢個敗登呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79e22698d676f17a00552ed5ef0d13c6d6cd7b3","tid":2350123,"uid":166080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"30677e207ec66df3925dfb17805cfa70c77ff8b8","tid":2350123,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7dbc643ddda5d492c824ef1278d278611ce6de9","tid":2350123,"uid":59898,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n咁追究到佢未？<br />\n成班大國都係縮頭龜，講經咩撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"追咩究<br />\n一年後先黎做場大龍鳳<br />\n最後乜結果都冇<br />\n配合佢果套源頭唔一定係中國"},{"pid":"eaa6ba8db96779d46ea5dc8411f76fa1b3f5adce","tid":2350123,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"又一證明武漢肺炎病毒係支共整出來 再刻意放毒"},{"pid":"0549c958f9d27fa1d399b6d2806c2a8cc9802fe5","tid":2350123,"uid":282359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7dbc643ddda5d492c824ef1278d278611ce6de9","tid":2350123,"uid":59898,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T05:36:01.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n咁追究到佢未？<br />\n成班大國都係縮頭龜，講經咩撚樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:06:28.000Z","msg":"過左成年啦。都仲唔郁鳩支那。<br />\n成班都垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是撚但啦你哋班鬼佬死之嘛。咪唔好撚郁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a7d65903425c712426d8848643a322ea0af0717","tid":2350123,"uid":111425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"其實佢最成功果點係將武漢肺炎夾硬洗左個名做物鳩新冠肺炎<br />\n依點真係好撚聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e835d4df87525a25390005801c8a14018af457","tid":2350123,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2a7d65903425c712426d8848643a322ea0af0717","tid":2350123,"uid":111425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T06